  <name>Zodiac</name>
  <summary>A simple program for plotting horoscopes</summary>
  <description>
    <p>The application generates horoscopes in svg and txt format. The user only needs to fill in the required fields. The application can make horoscopes for both one and two people.</p>
  </description>
